# Agri/Koli Marathi Phi-2 Fine-tuning with Unsloth 🌾🐟

This notebook is pre-configured for **Kaggle (T4 x2 or P100)** to fine-tune **Phi-2 (2.7B)** on the **Agri/Koli Marathi** dataset using **Unsloth (LoRA/4-bit)**.

---

